data.text:
Almost 60 hours later: still nothing else. Hopefully I'm in the clear. 

Sorry, but not sorry, that this was boring as fuck. Yay.

30 mins shy of 24 hours: my arm is about as sore as it was with the first dose/last night--not noticable & not preventing me from doing anything, or even from sleeping on that side.  Nothing else yet. I'm not really saying I'm in the clear yet to err on the side of caution.

12 hours later, still nothing so far. Only a tiny bit of soreness, but it wasnt noticable until Hawke whacked my arm with one of his toys. 

We'll see if the morning brings me anything.
@QueenRageNLove Somewhere, an anti-vaxxer is surprised it didn't immediately kill you.
About 5 hours later, doing fine. Been keeping my arm moving just like I did with the first shot. It prevents it from being sore. But nothing of note yet!
